=Description=

"Balaji S. Srinivasan is an angel investor and entrepreneur. Formerly the CTO of Coinbase and General Partner at Andreessen Horowitz, he was also the cofounder of Earn.com (acquired by Coinbase), Counsyl (acquired by Myriad), Teleport (acquired by Topia), and Coin Center.

In this talk, moderated by Shreyas Hariharan and powered by Devfolio and the Ethereum Foundation, Balaji speaks about the motivations for building the Network State, how to go about it, and addresses the promise that crypto adoption holds for the world with a focus on India."


